HAI 1.4
    CAN HAS STRING?

    HOW IZ I reverz YR s
        I HAS A len ITZ I IZ STRING'Z LEN YR s MKAY
        I HAS A result ITZ ""
        I HAS A i ITZ DIFF OF len AN 1
        IM IN YR loop NERFIN YR i TIL BOTH SAEM i AN -1
            I HAS A ch ITZ I IZ STRING'Z AT YR s AN YR i MKAY
            result R SMOOSH result AN ch MKAY
        IM OUTTA YR loop
        FOUND YR result
    IF U SAY SO

    VISIBLE I IZ reverz YR "CHEEZBURGER" MKAY
KTHXBYE
